      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">
          Insurance Change <span class="text-primary-600">2025/2026</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600">
          Deadlines, switching steps, and smart ways to save before 1 January 2026. Clear guidance for professionals and English speakers in Switzerland.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <button onclick="showConsultationModal()" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 rounded-md text-white bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 shadow-lg">
            Get Free Consultation
          </button>
          <a href="/health-insurance#compare" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 rounded-md text-primary-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 shadow-lg border border-gray-200">
            Compare Providers
          </a>
        </div>
