          <div class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Guaranteed acceptance for basic insurance (KVG/LAMal)</div>
          <div class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Change model/deductible with current insurer by <strong>31 December</strong></div>
          <div class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Biggest savings: high deductible + GP/HMO/Telmed + remove accident if employed</div>
          <div class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Keep subsidies: inform canton/insurer after switching</div>
        </div>
