        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 p-6">
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">October 2025</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Premiums Announced</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">Check new premiums by canton, age, model, and deductible. Start comparisons.</p>
