        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-5 border border-gray-200"><div class="text-primary-600 font-semibold">3. Apply</div><div class="text-gray-700 mt-1">Submit new application. Basic insurance is guaranteed acceptance.</div></div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-5 border border-gray-200"><div class="text-primary-600 font-semibold">4. Cancel</div><div class="text-gray-700 mt-1">Send written termination to current insurer by 30 Nov.</div></div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-5 border border-gray-200"><div class="text-primary-600 font-semibold">5. Confirm</div><div class="text-gray-700 mt-1">Receive confirmation; inform canton for subsidies if applicable.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <button onclick="showConsultationModal()" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-md text-white bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 shadow">Get Help Switching</button>
      </div>
    </div>
